snippet.title: HASTE: Broken Worlds - WISHLIST ON STEAM! 🏃🏽
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1796470/HASTE_Broken_Worlds/
Sign up for news about HASTE: http://runfastgame.com
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/HasteBrokenWorlds/

Run fast, leap through the air, and perfect your landings as you try again and again to make your way through an infinite number of worlds falling apart behind you!
